  "texts": [
    "Moreover, using inaccurate or misleading prompts can produce false and deceptive information in AI models.",
    "To address this issue, Bozkurt and Sharma (2023) proposed a set of strategies for designing precise prompts necessary for obtaining the desired output.",
    "These recommendations entail setting clear objectives, employing appropriate language and tone, providing context, examples, and references, specifying the expected output format, and incorporating essential details anticipated in the response.",
    "Additionally, fine-tuning prompts, experimenting with different variations, rigorously testing them to analyze results, and adjusting prompts based on desired responses can mitigate the generation of irrelevant or erroneous outputs and enhance overall performance (Bozkurt & Sharma, 2023).Another common issue encountered in prompt engineering and item generation is explainability.",
    "The European Commission (2019) stresses the significance of providing insights into how a specific AI algorithm operates and makes decisions."
  ],
